caption:
Discovering why you are the way you are is a powerful thing. Our very own @brocknowell led a powerful discussion within the UNTD Leadership. 
-
Everyone took time to think through 4 total events. 2 negative and 2 positives that helped shape us into who we are today. This was a hard yet rewarding activity that caused everyone to dig deep. 
-
Awareness into who we are and how we got here creates are clearer pathway forward into who we want to become.
